HELP on CLEARCHAN                            Level %L

  Syntax: /msg %N clearchan <channel> <parameters>

 Example: /msg %N clearchan #idle mbvo

   Usage: Clears a channel of either ops, modes, voiced users, bans, kicks all
          users, or glines all users -- or any combination of the above.
          
          Valid flags are the following:
             m: clears all channel modes
             k: kicks all users
             o: deops all users
             v: voices all users
             b: clears all bans
             g: g-lines all users
